WEBVTT

00:04:59.529 --> 00:05:02.435
Kognitiv rivojlanishga nima deysiz?

00:05:03.904 --> 00:05:05.383
"Biz mashinalarni qanchalik

00:05:05.407 --> 00:05:07.468
aqlli qila olamiz?" deb so'rashni o'rniga,

00:05:07.492 --> 00:05:08.665
keling, "Ular bizni

00:05:08.689 --> 00:05:11.394
qanchalik aqlli qilishi mumkin?" 
deb so'raylik.

00:05:13.105 --> 00:05:14.885
Misol sifatida xotirani olaylik.

00:05:15.511 --> 00:05:18.457
Xotira bu inson intellektining asosidir.

00:05:19.767 --> 00:05:22.738
Lekin inson xotirasi kamchilikka egaligi 
hammaga ma'lum.

00:05:23.541 --> 00:05:25.615
Biz hikoya qilishda yaxshimiz, ammo uning

00:05:25.639 --> 00:05:27.590
detallarida unchalik emas.

00:05:27.614 --> 00:05:30.820
Va bizning xotiramiz vaqt o'tishi 
bilan sustlashadi.